overview: Raaja Meeru Keka is a Telugu movie starring Revanth, Lasya, Noel and Taraka Ratna in prominent roles. The movie also stars RJ Hemanth and Shobitha. It is a drama directed by Krishna Kishore T and produced by Raaj Kumar M, with Sri Charan as the musician, forming part of the crew.
title: Raaja Meeru Keka
